Two sisters are dead after drowning in their bathtub. 

Sabrina and Savannah Russo of Pearland, Texas were found unresponsive on February 17, with Savannah dying later that day and Sabrina being taken off of life support late Sunday night.

Now, police are conducting an investigation and an autopsy is underway to figure out just what happened to the two girls, who were just 15-months old.

